<TEXT>
<P>
Mayim Bialik is one of the most talented young actresses on television today. 
The pilot episode of NBC's "Blossom" was excellent. And what a treat to watch 
the Fox comedy "Molloy." 
</P>
<P>
James Edward Rodriguez, 
</P>
<P>
Los Angeles 
</P>
