<HEADLINE>
<P>
CURRENTS: A GUIDE TO THE BEST OF SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA; 
</P>
<P>
SHOPTALK; 
</P>
<P>
SESAME STREET GOES RETAIL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LIKE other show- biz stars, Big Bird, Bert, Ernie and the rest of the gang are 
now bi-coastal. 
</P>
<P>
The Sesame Street General Store -- the first of its kind anywhere -- opens this 
month in the South Coast Plaza, showcasing puppets, books and other products. 
Kids will feel right at home; the store re-creates Bert and Ernie's apartment, 
at 123 Sesame Street, and Mr. Hooper's General Store. 
</P>
<P>
Sesame Street General Store, South Coast Plaza, 3333 Bristol St., Costa Mesa; 
(714) 241-1700. 
</P>
</TEXT>
