<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE POWER OF KIEV 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Greg Braxton's Aug. 19 article "The Graying of KABC" was most interesting, and 
we at KIEV add our congratulations to George Green and his crew. 
</P>
<P>
After 17 years with a very successful talk format at KIEV, we are sorry that 
the author did not stop by for a talk with us. We could have cleared up a 
serious misstatement when he wrote that we are "smaller, less powerful" when, 
in fact, our 10,000-watt power is twice the 5,000 watts at KABC. 
</P>
<P>
DICK SINCLAIR 
</P>
