<HEADLINE>
<P>
TRAIN TO MUNICH ROBBED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
MUNICH, West Germany 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Bandits pulled the emergency brake on a high-speed express train en route from 
Prague, Czechoslovakia, to Munich on Friday, sprayed tear gas and robbed the 
passengers, officials said. 
</P>
