</P>
<P>
THE SILICON SLEUTH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SURELOCK lost $230 Saturday when Meadow's Interco finished fifth in the fifth 
race. 
</P>
<P>
However, the loss didn't short circuit the computer's electronic enthusiasm for 
today's card, which features a turf triple header. 
</P>
<P>
SURELOCK's bets are $20 to win and place on Freya Stark in the third race, $40 
to win and place on Final Forecast in the fifth race and $100 to win and place 
on Classic Fame in the simulcast Arlington Million. 
</P>
