</P>
<P>
NONFICTION 
</P>
<P>
I WANT TO GROW HAIR, I WANT TO GROW UP, I WANT TO GO TO BOISE by Erma Bombeck 
(HarperCollins: $5.50). Young cancer patients share their fondest desires, 
humor and fears with the emphatic writer. 
</P>
<P>
