celebration. IRIS SCHNEIDER / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Cuica Calli Indians 
from Jalisco, Mexico, dress in costume. Festival director Peter Sellars urged 
people to attend "to get an inundation of beauty." RANDY LEFFINGWELL / Los 
Angeles Times 
</P>
