Arrowhead fire -- The Times reported incorrectly Sunday that a San Bernardino 
County Fire Agency investigator said a weekend blaze that destroyed four homes 
in Lake Arrowhead was "definitely arson." The official said only that there was 
an arson investigation. A spokesman for the Arrowhead Fire District, Paul 
Nyerick, said investigators have found the point of origin of the fire "but the 
cause is undetermined, with suspicious circumstances." 
</P>
