himself. Page 10 ; Photo, The writer in his garden, wearing a Colombian ruana 
-- a man of much genius and many contradictions. Ruven Afanador; Photo, The 
author, about 2 years old here, was one of 15 children. ; Photo, Garcia 
Marquez, with Castro in 1982, believes the leader is Cuba's only hope. ; Photo, 
